"   <div class=\"block pha drugH1Div\" id=\"F186092\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Mechanism of Action",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Exhibits noncompetitive H",
"     <sub>",
"      1",
"     </sub>",
"     -receptor antagonist and mast cell stabilizer properties. Efficacy in conjunctivitis likely results from a combination of anti-inflammatory and antihistaminergic actions including interference with chemokine-induced migration of eosinophils into inflamed conjunctiva.",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block phk drugH1Div\" id=\"F186105\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
